Description: HaLOS Cockpit configuration and branding
 This package provides HaLOS-specific configuration for the Cockpit
 web interface, including branding (logo, CSS, favicon), Homarr dashboard
 integration, and mDNS subdomain advertisement for cockpit.{hostname}.local.
